summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2472, for the improvement of 35th Avenue Southwest from West Oregon Street to Roxbury Street, all in the City of Seattle, by grading and curbing the same, and providing for the necessary surface drainage, under Ordinance No. 26813 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
